{"tid":829725,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（懺悔）小時候錯手殺生經驗","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T17:27:22.000Z","uid":6031,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71c0a50aa1b4c72a2670ba39604f5c812a966a34","tid":829725,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起細個害死咗好多動物<br />\n應該都喺6-9歲呢段期間<br />\n大個諗返轉頭好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但細個真係唔識<br />\n<br />\n金魚：老豆養，成日食完龜苓膏就拎個罐不啲魚出黎，想幫佢著衫（用糖紙），試過幾次，後來有次著著下衫佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴西龜：都係老豆養嘅，屋企仲養咗好大缸熱帶魚呀珊瑚咁。睇完海底奇兵覺得啲龜同魚傾計好可愛，好想睇佢哋互動，就將隻巴西龜掉咗落魚缸，見佢游黎游去仲以為佢好開心，係咁叫佢搵mo仔同多莉，第日佢浮屍水面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n草蜢：喺公園玩捉依因嗰陣見到地下有兩隻草蜢痴埋一齊，後面嗰隻搭住咗前面嗰隻，唔知佢哋做緊乜（大個諗返，應該扑緊嘢⋯⋯），一手蚊走咗後面嗰隻，帶咗佢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵個杯仔養住佢，想落公園帶埋佢同伴返黎，見到俾人踩扁咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返到屋企發現本身捉住嗰隻唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問老豆，佢話沖咗落廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四腳爬爬：喺後樓梯見到，又捉咗返屋企，放咗喺隻大碗到，諗住入廚房拎麵包俾佢食，出返廳唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望望下見到佢爬咗去窗邊，我大叫：唔好呀蛇蛇！！（類似啦唔太記得），下一秒佢爬出啲，一嘢吹鬼咗落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （屋企39樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有次就冇殺生<br />\n<br />\n有隻麻雀飛咗入屋，嗰陣搬咗去9樓高嘅樓，隻雀仲自己飛去個獲入面，老母：嘩，加餸呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我決心阻止老母（嗰陣唔知佢講笑），就將隻麻雀帶咗入自己房，用個盒仔裝住，後來發現佢有隻腳仔好似行唔到，我就捉佢出黎，用較剪cut咗自己件衫一忽仔，綁住佢隻腳（睇卡通片係咁樣救啲斷手腳嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），唔俾老母踏足我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後襯老母出街偷咗佢床頭櫃啲錢，去附近買咗個雀籠養住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母問點解有，我話我執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過咗一段時間，有日朝早捉佢出黎抹身，發現佢行得走得，就抱佢去窗邊，佢就飛走咗lu"},{"pid":"2bd1c39e10b1507ab79d3eb0662d581ba60250f1","tid":829725,"uid":6031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"對唔住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你哋有好好投胎，做咗啲有人愛錫嘅動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a9c58aadb635c80f968e726868000f196f3a78","tid":829725,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"食抗生素 殺菌"},{"pid":"89d7aedbe46303842d844f726a2cf8ea0cb39253","tid":829725,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"1) 特登買d魚仔，魚苗個d，都成幾十條，逐條逐條玩死佢地，睇住佢地無水係到彈下彈下，又捉返佢入水，見佢未死又捉返出黎，最尾個幾條通常特別好生命力，就估下邊條死先，最後，一個鐘唔洗，玩死晒d魚仔<br />\n<br />\n2) 買左兩隻龜返黎，餓死晒佢地，仲要其實我好耐都無餵野佢地食，但佢地好耐都唔死，最後死左(可能呀爸呀媽幫手餵呢個真係唔知)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家打隻甲由，都會手起刀落，盡快殺死佢，希望佢死個陣唔好咁痛苦。真係罪孽深重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f15d9f74c0e68b63b131ac5590ad79beaf9b27","tid":829725,"uid":206540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c0a50aa1b4c72a2670ba39604f5c812a966a34","tid":829725,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起細個害死咗好多動物<br />\n應該都喺6-9歲呢段期間<br />\n大個諗返轉頭好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但細個真係唔識<br />\n<br />\n金魚：老豆養，成日食完龜苓膏就拎個罐不啲魚出黎，想幫佢著衫（用糖紙），試過幾次，後來有次著著下衫佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴西龜：都係老豆養嘅，屋企仲養咗好大缸熱帶魚呀珊瑚咁。睇完海底奇兵覺得啲龜同魚傾計好可愛，好想睇佢哋互動，就將隻巴西龜掉咗落魚缸，見佢游黎游去仲以為佢好開心，係咁叫佢搵mo仔同多莉，第日佢浮屍水面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n草蜢：喺公園玩捉依因嗰陣見到地下有兩隻草蜢痴埋一齊，後面嗰隻搭住咗前面嗰隻，唔知佢哋做緊乜（大個諗返，應該扑緊嘢⋯⋯），一手蚊走咗後面嗰隻，帶咗佢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵個杯仔養住佢，想落公園帶埋佢同伴返黎，見到俾人踩扁咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返到屋企發現本身捉住嗰隻唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問老豆，佢話沖咗落廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四腳爬爬：喺後樓梯見到，又捉咗返屋企，放咗喺隻大碗到，諗住入廚房拎麵包俾佢食，出返廳唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望望下